high_descs: Step to the left to face the tea pot on the counter.
Pick up the tea pot on the counter.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Put the tea pot in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn right to face the shelves.
Place the tea pot on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: To clean a tea pot and put it on the shelf.

high_descs: Take a step left and then walk to the counter.
Pick up the tea pot that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the counter then take a step right.
Wash the tea pot in the sink then pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelves at the end of the counter and turn right to face them.
Put the tea pot to the right of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot on the shelf.

high_descs: turn left, walk to the counter by the stove
grab the kettle on the counter
turn right, walk to the sink
put the kettle in the sink, wash the kettle with water, take the kettle out
turn around, walk to the shelf on the right
put the kettle on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: wash the kettle in the sink, put the kettle on the shelf

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward, then turn right towards the granite counter top.
Pick up the tea kettle on the granite counter top.
Turn around, turn left and walk to the sink.
Rinse the tea kettle in the sink.
Turn around, walk across the room, then turn right.
Place the tea kettle on the brown shelf next to the granite counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tea kettle on the shelf.

high_descs: Take a step to the left and face the counter.
Pick up the leftmost tea kettle.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn around walk straight until the wall. Turn right and face the shelving unit.
Place the kettle on the second to bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed kettle on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step then turn right and face the counter near the tea pot.
Pick up the tea pot off of the counter.
Turn around and walk to position yourself in front of the sink so you are facing it.
Put the tea pot in the sink and run the water and wash it.
Walk back over to the counter where you were before except move yourself slightly to the left so you are in front of the brown shelves.
Place the tea pot towards the right of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed tea pot on the shelf.
